
# ğŸµ Spotify to Navidrome Downloader  

## ğŸ“– Overview  
This project sets up **Navidrome** as a personal music streaming server and includes a **Python script** to download and organize music from Spotify playlists/albums (via YouTube using `yt-dlp`).  

It automatically places music in the Navidrome library so you can stream it anywhere.  

